items.name: COMMERCE_CONTINUE_AS_GUEST
items.purpose: Stores the user's preference (true/false) to continue checking out an order as a guest. Strictly necessary.

items.name: COMPANY_ID
items.purpose: Stores the company ID to associate the user with an instance. Strictly necessary.

items.name: CONSENT_TYPE_FUNCTIONAL
items.purpose: Stores the end user's consent option (true/false) for functional cookies to remember the user's preference. Strictly necessary.

items.name: CONSENT_TYPE_NECESSARY
items.purpose: Stores the end user's consent option (true/false) for necessary cookies to ensure essential functionality. Strictly necessary.

items.name: CONSENT_TYPE_PERFORMANCE
items.purpose: Stores the end user's consent option (true/false) for performance cookies to manage performance-related preferences. Strictly necessary.

items.name: CONSENT_TYPE_PERSONALIZATION
items.purpose: Stores the end user's consent option (true/false) for personalization cookies to manage personalized content and settings. Strictly necessary.

items.name: COOKIE_SUPPORT
items.purpose: Stores the user's preference (true/false) to store cookies in the browser. Strictly necessary.

items.name: HIGHLIGHTED_COMMENT_ID_KEY
items.purpose: Stores the highlighted fragment comment's ID when entering the page editor from a comment notification. Strictly necessary.

items.name: ID
items.purpose: Stores the encrypted user ID to remember the user's login details when the 'Remember Me' option is enabled. Strictly necessary.

items.name: JSESSIONID
items.purpose: Stores a unique identifier to maintain the user's session on the server. Strictly necessary.

items.name: LFR_SESSION_STATE_userID
items.purpose: Stores a timestamp and the unencrypted user ID in the cookie name to manage session invalidation or auto-extension when the 'Remember Me' option is enabled. Strictly necessary.

items.name: SERVER_ID
items.purpose: Stores the web server ID to keep the user connected to the same Liferay instance with access to the session and cached data. Strictly necessary.

items.name: access_token
items.purpose: Stores a unique access token to identify the logged-in user in the Liferay Cloud console. Strictly necessary.

items.name: com.liferay.commerce.model.CommerceOrder#groupId
items.purpose: Stores an order ID to link it to the account the guest creates later. Strictly necessary.

items.name: com.liferay.commerce.model.CommerceOrder#groupId
items.purpose: Stores the order ID of the contextual order to use while punching out. Strictly necessary.

items.name: com.liferay.search.experiences.web_successMessage
items.purpose: Stores a localized success message briefly when a Search Blueprints blueprint or element is saved, so the message can be displayed on a different page. Strictly necessary.

items.name: connect.sid
items.purpose: Stores a session ID to identify a single session in the Liferay Cloud backend infrastructure. Strictly necessary.

items.name: modalExperienceState
items.purpose: Stores the state of the modal when creating a new experience. Strictly necessary.
